column4:
To add student information, follow these steps: 
1. Enter the official CPHOS mini-program. 
2. Click on "My" -> "Candidate Information". 
3. Click "Add Candidate Information", then enter the student's name, choose their grade, select any historical awards, and click "Confirm". 
4. Repeat the operation until all student information is entered. 
5. To modify or delete student information, click "Edit" to modify or "Delete" to remove.
